➜宽哥：《临江仙》
http://www.sohu.com/a/420808323_100115135	26286
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200925/c9d7e1d282d5495c9c198d313bc18437.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《临江仙》词林正韵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 原文/宽哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万里云霞归路，风尘南陌行人。烟波迢递急如焚。别蒲舟水疾，乡近笑声闻。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">二老别来无恙？遥思每欲销魂。几番秋去又迎春。怡然方外乐，鹤发益精神！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200925/a636b5ba247d4b0b83a5f27cccd0105d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200925/49498a520d1847cd835f61a9a9e93306.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
