➜广东诗人小隐：围炉四秋
http://www.sohu.com/a/420809713_100115135	26701
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200925/005cb06abed94a8b8e5a3cb30977d9b2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>围炉四秋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/小隐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诗意围炉过四秋，酒杯多日竟迟留。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">休言白发难堪老，且看红颜枉自愁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为赋新词重问道，谁将旧事暂寻幽。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">偷闲识得无忧计，枕上清辉月入楼。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200925/5774dbbed6bd455bbdd6c4cfd96865e9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>小隐，自由职业者，一个游走人间的过客，喜欢用文字与灵魂对话的小女人，左手柴米油盐酱拌醋～右手诗词歌赋花间茶～</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200925/b7390ac14e1846ea89b8c18b3686f096.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
