➜听尘居士：人间行
http://www.sohu.com/a/420812347_100115135	27352
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200925/24140bd0e11549b995862c13d7f75ded.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>人间行</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/听尘居士</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长空朝阳映山碧，早蹬高台西风凉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">历数人间冷暖事，忽做少年敢轻狂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200925/a025826ea9c44e20919f990f1ebbc88c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>听尘居士，原名牛喜忠。吉林籍，现居深圳。半生无所成，流浪江湖。偶弄笔墨，未有一名。闲了拈花惹草，迎来半院春色；静时参禅打坐，佛道一通乱修。朋友小聚可品香茗，饮自酿美酒，临厨而成美食。唯不懂人间烟火，只好浪迹天涯一隅。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200925/b93e595aa3454fc694408b4ec78a5925.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
